summarized_story:
Popular clergyman of the Christ Apostolic Church, Prophet Samuel Abiara, has paid a condolence visit to the widow of popular televangelist, T.B Joshua.
T.B Joshua, the founder and senior pastor of Synagogue, Church of All Nations died last Saturday, June 5th and popular Nigerian clergyman, Abiara visited the bereaved wife, Evelyn Joshua in her home to condole with her.
